Text: Just wanted to let you knowNonPrivilegedpst we are leaving for Estes tomorrow and will not be back until the following Sunday You can call Wills cell if you need us or call the Snyders in Estes I am doing fine The baby is kicking and ready to cool off in Colorado I will chat with you when we get back We love you guys

HelloNonPrivilegedpst I hope everyone is safe What a crazy frightening day I spoke with Mom and Dad and they wanted me to let yall know that they are not sure if they will be flying back from Vegas tomorrow or not It all depends on what happens next They will email you when they get back Love to you all PS I still have weeks to go
